---
title: Asian Snow Pea & Mint Slaw with Roasted Peanuts | Serves 2
description: This colourful Asian-style slaw is all about texture and flavour. We've added all the crunch to our ready-to-go slaw mix,
with snow peas and roasted peanuts.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/60501c9c9606d85bfb32609a-11f0d486.jpg
